description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '25 MIN FEEL GOOD PILATES || At-Home Pilates Workout (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
